2011-09-08T09:30:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/mpi-corp-august-sales-fall-8-81-table-6223-tt.html
MPI CORP (6223)  said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 8.81% to NT$328,620,000 from NT$360,378,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            328,620          360,378    
YOY%              -8.81%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,759,891        2,055,373   
YOY%              34.28% 
=================================================================
 